game.name: Princesses at World Championship 2018
game.description:
Wow, even two of your favorite Disney princesses Elsa and Rapunzel love playing soccer games during their free hours! They do not miss even a single match when the World Championship 2018 is going on. In order to enjoy the spirit of their favorite team, they love putting on the same dresses as the team they support to wear. These two cute princesses again want to choose the outfits for celebrating this evening. Join Princesses At World Championship 2018 and be prepared to get them ready for the event in the evening!

Hurry up friends! The biggest match of the world championship is going to take place tonight. Rapunzel is a big fan of Great Britain so try to choose a white and blue casual top and pair it up with a white and black striped skirt. Complete her look with a cute red and blue color cap on her head along with the necessary accessories in this brand new girls game!

Make sure that your chosen outfit follows the color codes like white, blue, and red and are comfortable as well. 
Span is the team Elsa supports so she seeks a dress available in red, green and yellow color. Find a printed top in her wardrobe and match it with a blue jacket, a pair of green color sport pants, a green scarf, a blue jacket and a pink backpack in this html5 dressing game! We are pretty sure that these two beauties will love the dresses you chose for them. Play more popular titles from the category of free girls games and have fun with your friends without download!
